						We utilize that data to improve user experience and additionally monitor the Site preventing fraud and inappropriate content or behavior. We may likewise gather supplemental data got from third parties, for example, navigation and demographic information.
					</p>
					<p>We may gather information about you when you connect with Us on any social media networks (Including but not limited to Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Instagram, Google+, YouTube) where We maintain our official profiles. The information about you, available on your publicly visible social profile may be collected. Once you Contact Us (by any means), our Sales and Marketing Team may collect your information from commercially
						available sources such as data aggregators and public databases to provide you with the better solutions.
