					<p>We are currently using Google Analytics and Hotjar. Google Analytics and Hotjar collect information and report website trends without identifying individual visitors. Google Analytics and Hotjar use their own cookies to track visitor interactions and behavior to help website owners to view a variety of reports and recordings about visitor's interaction with the website. Please see the following links for more information
					</p>
					<p>For Google Analytics: http://www.google.com/analytics/ and http://www.google.com/privacy.html and you can opt out of being included in Google Analytics here.
