					<h3>4. How we use your information</h3>
					<p>Personal Information you submit to Us is utilized either to respond to requests that you make or to help Us in serving you better. We use your Personal Information in the following ways: to identify you as a user, to provide the Service you request, respond to your inquiries and requests, for our internal research and development, to improve our Site and Services, to customize content to match your preferences, to ask for ratings and reviews of our Services, and to detect and prevent fraud, spam, abuse, security incidents, and other harmful activity.
					</p>
					<p>We use your contact number(s), e-mail ID(s), Other information (provided by you or based on your publicly available information) or any third party to communicate with you directly or to discuss your business requirement with you. We use your e-mail ID(s) to send you invoice receipts, reminders, transactional e-mails, periodic promotional or non-promotional e-mail (including information about ProDesigns or partner campaigns and Services), notifications, surveys, newsletters, offers, and other promotional materials related to our Services.
