					<p>Regardless of any choices, 941Digital may disclose Personal Information if it believes in good faith that such disclosure is necessary (a) to comply with relevant laws or to respond to subpoenas or warrants served on 941Digital (b) in connection with any legal investigation; (c) to protect or defend the rights or property of 941Digital or users of the Services; and/or (d) to assist or investigate in preventing any violation of the law, the User Agreement or this Privacy Policy.
