					<h3>c. Deletion or Changes to Personal Information</h3>
					<p>You can obtain a copy of your Personal Information, rectify inaccurate details, erase, export and restrict your Personal Information at any time by e-mailing Us at legal@941Digital.com. We will respond to your request to access within 30 days. You can object to our processing of your Personal Information at any time. Contact our Data Protection Officer with requests or concerns at legal@941Digital.com. In addition to the above, If you are not satisfied with the response, you have the right to complain with supervisory authority for data protection.
					</p>
					<p>In case of account or information deletion, We may be required to keep this information, and not delete it, for a certain time, as needed to provide you Services, for fraud prevention & similar purposes and as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
