					<p>Upon request, 941Digital will provide you with information about whether We hold any of your Personal Information. You may review, access, update, correct, or remove your information at any time. Please Contact Us at legal@941Digital.com with your name, e-mail ID and details of the information which you want to access, update or remove.
					</p>
					<p>Once We receive the request, We will investigate the matter and correct any inaccuracies or remove it as soon as possible where necessary or guide you to update it quickly or to delete it - unless We have to keep that information for legal purposes or legitimate business, for fraud prevention, to provide you Services and similar purposes, to resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
					</p>
					<p>Please note that if your access of using the Service being ceased or you have ceased your access, then you may no longer have the ability to access or request to update your information.
